HEADWORD: Unfrequented
<hw>Un`fre*quent"ed</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref. <ets>un-</ets> +
<ets>frequented</ets>.]</ety> <def>Rarely visited; seldom or never
resorted to by human beings; <as>as, an <ex>unfrequented</ex> place or
forest</as>.</def> <rj><au>Addison.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

